# Optional override for API / WebSocket base (no path). When unset in __DEV__, the app
# derives the host from Metro (expo hostUri + bundle scriptURL) so physical devices use
# your Mac's LAN IP automatically. Set this if auto-detection fails or you use a tunnel.
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.105:8000
# EXPO_PUBLIC_WS_BASE_URL=ws://192.168.1.105:8083
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=
